       <div class="uu-main-content">
        <hr/>
        <p class="text-callout-md text-center">
         By offering a variety of events, programs and services, Student Leadership &amp; Involvement
                           at the University of Utah incites students to action, encourages engagement in campus
                           and community service, and provide opportunities that enrich and support personal
                           and academic growth and development, which culminates in a lifelong commitment to
                           effective leadership.
        </p>
        <hr/>
        <div class="row equal-height ">
         <!-- start column 1-->
         <div class="col-2-eq-height">
          <div class="" id="ss">
           <div id="default_banner">
            <a class="" href="/index.php" target="">
             <img alt="Student Leadership &amp; Involvement University of Utah" height="301" src="/_images/banners/websitebanner.jpg" width="878"/>
