              <img alt="" height="881" src="/_images/staff_photos/fall2018/teamphoto.jpg" width="1583"/>
             </a>
            </h2>
            <h2 style="text-align: center;">
             Meet the Team
            </h2>
            <p>
             The Student Leadership &amp; Involvement team is always happy to help you find involvement
                                       and help you become a better leader.  Please reach out to us and let us know what
                                       we can do to help!
            </p>
